input_str: "Tell Me Your Wish (Genie)" (Hangul: 소원을 말해봐; RR: Sowoneul malhaebwa) is a song recorded by South Korean girl group Girls' Generation for their second extended play (EP) of the same name (2009). It was released on June 22, 2009 as a single from the EP. Written by Dsign Music, Fridolin Nordso Schjoldan, and Yoo Young-jin,
